name: Space Gate
summary:
Space Gate
Protect the last refuge of humanity

Step into the role of a Security Officer aboard a massive spaceship refuge. Humans and mutants arrive seeking safety but some hide dangerous intentions. Inspect carefully. Decide fast.

Scan and inspect

Use futuristic tools to detect hidden items, check temperatures, and compare identities with wanted lists. One mistake can put everyone at risk.
